column5: Heading up to the Minden area this week, thought I would try Boshkung Lake for lakers, usng a portable hut.  Anyone known where we can get access and parking?  thanks,  Brian

I can't be positive as I avioded Bosh during the time I lived in the area but I am sure there was a few spots along the side of the highway that I used to see vehicles parked. Some of the Lindsay folk should know...like I said I never fished it, drove by it lots though!!!
